name: One Proud Owner
description:
Astro looking extremely proud of his
new donut powered porsche 917K.
What more do you need in life... than a
porsche, a pack of donuts and some
inflatable flamingo friends. Digital
Illustration from the Astro & the
Universe series by mbsjq. 1/1, Single
Edition. [Bonus] Signed mbsjq print
included.
